# 💾 6. Logging System (MVP)

## 🎯 Purpose:

Keep simple history of reports

---

## 🔹 Option A (Simplest)

* Store last report in memory

---

## 🔹 Option B (Better MVP)

Save as text file:

```java
File file = new File(getFilesDir(), "report.txt");
FileOutputStream fos = new FileOutputStream(file);
fos.write(reportString.getBytes());
```

---

## 🔹 Naming Strategy

```text
report_YYYYMMDD_HHMM.txt
```

---

# 📤 7. Share / Export

## 🔧 Share Intent

```java
Intent intent = new Intent(Intent.ACTION_SEND);
intent.setType("text/plain");
intent.putExtra(Intent.EXTRA_TEXT, reportString);
startActivity(intent);
```

---

