# ⚠️ 8. Error Handling

| Case           | Handling        |
| -------------- | --------------- |
| Sensor missing | "Not Available" |
| No sensor data | "No Data"       |
| Test skipped   | "Skipped"       |
| API restricted | Skip silently   |

---

# ⏱️ 9. Execution Strategy (Important)

* Do NOT block UI thread
* Use:

```text
Handler / simple background thread
```

